@startuml

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor #F8F9FA
    BorderColor #495057
    ArrowColor #495057
    FontColor #212529
}
skinparam package {
    BackgroundColor #E9ECEF
    BorderColor #6C757D
}
skinparam activity {
    BackgroundColor #F8F9FA
    BorderColor #495057
    ArrowColor #495057
    FontColor #212529
    DiamondBackgroundColor #FFF3CD
    DiamondBorderColor #856404
    StartColor #212529
    EndColor #DC3545
    BarColor #495057
}
skinparam swimlane {
    BorderColor #6C757D
    TitleBackgroundColor #E9ECEF
    TitleFontColor #212529
    TitleFontSize 13
}

title Main Build Pipeline\n<size:11>(scripts/build.js — async build() orchestrator)</size>

|Orchestrator|
start
:Invoke **build()** (async)\nResolve ROOT_DIR, DIST_DIR, buildDir;

|Sub-Pages & Static Site|
:Call **generateSubPages**(ROOT_DIR)\n<size:10>build-sub-pages.js → HTML for skills,\nanti-patterns, tutorials</size>;
:Collect **subPageFiles[]**\n<size:10>entry-points for Bun bundler</size>;
:Call **buildStaticSite**(subPageFiles)\n<size:10>Bun.build({ entrypoints: [index.html, cheatsheet.html,\nprivacy.html, ...subPageFiles], outdir: build/,\nminify: true, sourcemap: linked })</size>;

if (Bun build successful?) then (yes)
    if (build/public/ directory exists?) then (yes)
        :Flatten **build/public/*** → **build/**\n<size:10>Remove nested public dir</size>;
    else (no / skip)
    endif
else (no)
    :Log build errors;
    :Exit process (code 1);
    stop
endif

|Orchestrator|
:Copy root static assets\n<size:10>og-image.jpg, robots.txt, sitemap.xml,\nfavicon.svg, apple-touch-icon.png</size>;
note right
  Guarded copy:
  fs.existsSync(src) → copy
  else skip
end note
:Copy **antipattern-examples/** dir\n<size:10>public/antipattern-examples → build/antipattern-examples</size>;
:Copy **detect-antipatterns-browser.js**\n<size:10>src/ → build/js/</size>;

:Call **readSourceFiles**(ROOT_DIR) → **skills[]**\nCall **readPatterns**(ROOT_DIR) → **patterns{}**\n<size:10>utils.js: skills (name, description, userInvocable),\npatterns (patterns[], antipatterns[])\nRead skillsVersion from .claude-plugin/plugin.json</size>;

|Provider Transforms|
:Iterate **PROVIDERS** config list\n<size:10>scripts/lib/transformers/index.js</size>;

fork
    :Run **createTransformer**(config)\n<size:10>Emit dist/{provider}/\n(unprefixed)</size>;
fork again
    :Run **createTransformer**(config, prefix='i-')\n<size:10>Emit dist/{provider}-prefixed/\n(i- prefixed output)</size>;
end fork

:Call **assembleUniversal**(DIST_DIR)\n<size:10>Merge all provider configDirs → dist/universal/\nWrite README.txt</size>;
:Call **assembleUniversal**(DIST_DIR, '-prefixed')\n<size:10>Merge all provider configDirs → dist/universal-prefixed/\nWrite README.txt</size>;
:Call **createAllZips**(DIST_DIR)\n<size:10>zip.js → dist/*.zip\n(individual providers + universal)</size>;

|Orchestrator|
:Call **generateApiData**(buildDir, skills, patterns)\n<size:10>Emit build/_data/api/skills.json,\ncommands.json, patterns.json,\ncommand-source/{id}.json</size>;
:Call **copyDistToBuild**(DIST_DIR, buildDir)\n<size:10>Mirror dist/ → build/_data/dist/</size>;
:Call **generateCFConfig**(buildDir)\n<size:10>Write build/_headers,\nbuild/_redirects, build/_routes.json</size>;

:Sync skills to repo root for local testing\n<size:10>For each provider:\ncopyDirSync(dist/{provider}/{configDir}/skills → {configDir}/skills)</size>;
note right
  Guarded sync:
  skillsSrc exists AND skillsDest exists
  → rmSync then copyDirSync
end note
:Remove deprecated skill stubs\n<size:10>frontend-design, teach-impeccable, arrange,\nnormalize, onboard, extract\nfrom all local harness dirs</size>;

|Validation|
fork
    :Call **generateCounts**(ROOT_DIR, skills, buildDir)\n<size:10>Read detect-antipatterns.mjs for rule IDs\nWrite public/js/generated/counts.js\nValidate references in HTML/MD/JSON files</size>;
fork again
    :Call **validateAntipatternRules**(ROOT_DIR)\n<size:10>Parse ANTIPATTERNS[].skillGuideline\nCross-check against SKILL.md DON'T lines</size>;
fork again
    :Call **validateSiteHeader**(ROOT_DIR)\n<size:10>Check <!-- site-header v1 --> marker\nin 3 HTML pages</size>;
fork again
    :Call **validateNoEmDashes**(ROOT_DIR)\n<size:10>Scan content/site, public HTML,\nscripts for em-dash characters</size>;
end fork

if (Any validation errors?) then (countErrors > 0\nOR validationErrors > 0\nOR headerErrors > 0\nOR emDashErrors > 0)
    :Log validation failures;
    :Exit process (code 1)\n<size:10>Build artifacts already exist on disk</size>;
    stop
else (all pass)
    :Log **"✨ Build complete!"**;
endif

|Orchestrator|
stop

@enduml
